    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在史前地下世界中扮演安祖（Anzu），解决不断变化的谜题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源和宝藏，在中心购买升级！还可以在孵化场孵化恐龙蛋，获得额外奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要用尽一切手段取悦神灵，并确保生存！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在中心建造孵化场，孵化恐龙蛋以收集更多宝藏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将恐龙蛋放置在巢穴或孵化器上开始孵化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在中心通过匹配4个对象融合并升级孵化设备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索中心的各个部分，解锁更多升级！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光顾商店，可能会找到对冒险有用的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索并重建博物馆，发现未知的文物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级谜题，收集更多资源并挑战自我！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心……神灵会用尽一切来阻止你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解决不断变化的谜题</strong>，扮演安祖。</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong>中心</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索并重建</strong>博物馆</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级</strong>谜题</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>孵化恐龙蛋</strong>，获得额外奖励</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>融合</strong>建筑方块，升级版本</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁特殊角色</strong>进行游戏</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对危险挑战</strong>，难度会随着游戏进展而增加</p>[/]</ul>",
